rows.label: tlk44200185_01_msg0001
rows.name:
You! Outlander! Have you any books?
Any books? Books from the outside?

rows.label: tlk44200185_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Huff... My apologies. It's just
that I've read pretty much all I
could from the library already...

rows.label: tlk44200185_01_msg0003
rows.name:
So I thought that visitors from
the outside might have Invidian
books, or Superbian ones...

rows.label: tlk44200185_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I'd love to read some books from the
outside, but Luxuria won't have
anything to do with other countries.
